Package net.dean.jraw.models.meta

This package contains classes relevant to meta-evaluation and testing

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    JsonSerializer<B extends JsonModel>
    This class provides a standard interface for turning a Jackson JsonNode into a JRAW JsonModel
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ContributionSerializer
    This class is responsible for serializing Contribution subclasses.
    DefaultJsonSerializer
    This class attempts to serialize a JsonModel by invoking a constructor that takes a single JsonNode as an argument.
    MessageSerializer
    This class is responsible for serializing Message subclasses.
    ModelManager
    This class is responsible for managing the creation of JsonModels.
    SubmissionSerializer
    This class is responsible for serializing Submissions, since they are presented differently than other models.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Model.Kind
    A list of possible values of "kind" nodes from the reddit API
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    JsonProperty
    Used for testing purposes.
    Model
    This annotation is used to verify that the correct data is being mapped to the correct object.
